channel.title: The Rebirth of Project Cleanup [Last update June 10th]
channel.description:
[center][b][size=14pt]A Recent Announcement About Development.[/size][/b] The next version will be coming soon, I had to take a long break but now I'm healing up and I have time for this, expect a number of larger updates over the next few days. As of now [6/10/2011] I have added in full knife throwing support for npc's and players along with the fire and damage rates.
[b]Got a suggestion? Drop a post and tell me a little about it.[/b]
[/center]
[center][b]Info:[/b] *---------------* [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,438029.0.html]Files started with[/url] *---------------* [b]Update downloads[/b] [url=http://uppit.com/1wfwgfjn3jxz/Project_Cleanup.rar](v0.25)[/url] *---------------*[/center]
[center] [b]Current things being worked on for next version[/b] Finished Mostly done Just starting
[b]All magebook teleports to right area's[/b] [b]All fish cookable Cooking cakes Full smithing bars Full smelting ores Auto casting RuneCrafting Essence mine[/b] [b]Knife throwing[/b] [b]Teleport other spell Bones to Banana's Installing undamaged 317 cache [/b]
[b]Media:[/b]
[url=http://i1207.photobucket.com/albums/bb467/xandrwex/moparscape1.jpg][b]Current Log in Box[/b][/url] [/center]
[b]Updates in v0.25:[/b] [code] • April 25th, 11:28PM Removed Mp3 playing system from client *---------------* • April 25th, 11:37PM Removed screen shot system from client *---------------* • April 25th, 12:01AM Removed auto talker (who the hell put that in this in the first place?) *---------------* • April 26th, 12:10AM Removed custom cursors (no one wants to play with a stupid Kenny cursor.) *---------------* • April 26th, 12:31AM Removed world handler (theres only one world on private servers lol.) *---------------* • April 26th, 1:22AM Removed account handler (Useless stuff like chat effects that are already coded in.) *---------------* • April 26th, 1:24AM Removed old auto updater (reduces client load time.) *---------------* • April 26th, 7:10PM Removed glitched guard npc along with animations and models for it. *---------------* • April 26th, 10:26PM Removed non working mithril dragon along with animations and models. *---------------* • April 26th, 10:26PM Removed Avatar of Destruction npc. *---------------* • April 26th, 10:33PM Removed Avatar of Creation npc. *---------------* • April 26th, 10:35PM Removed tormented demons along with models *---------------* • April 26th, 11:20PM Removed, red, blue, green, black and king black dragon models and code *---------------* • April 26th, 11:27PM Removed Hill, Fire, Ice, and Moss Giants. *---------------* • April 27th, 5:03AM Removed 41 images from client not being used (total removed: 41) *---------------* • April 27th, 5:03AM Added updated tab images to client (this is just graphics.) *---------------* • April 27th, 5:08AM Fixed all emote on emote tab (except skill capes, thats coming as soon as I get the animations.) *---------------* • April 27th, 5:28AM New login box, background and button (just needed to make it not look crappy.) *---------------* • April 27th, 5:32AM Few small tweaks to how the client loads (now loads fully in 4 seconds, half the time as before.) *---------------* • April 27th, 6:14AM Removed lots of text from client loading screen, makes it look more smooth, added new login bar. *---------------* • April 27th, 9:48PM Removed Jagex's sound player (not the crappy blurrs one I removed before) *---------------* • May 3rd, 8:16PM Finished up cleaning gui.java, (Currently 151 lines and 4kb) (At start it was 1000+ lines and 30kb+, shows how much useless stuff is in a normal delta and bluurs client.) *---------------* • April 30th, 1:24PM Removed all global objects, coders will have to code their own homes and such. [/code]

item.title: The Rebirth of Project Cleanup [Last update June 10th]
item.dc:creator: @spearo spearo
item.description:
@spearo wrote:

IDK if its still in development but if it is here is my suggestion:

[quote=“Loveandpower, post:30, topic:392634”]Dont put teleports to exact locations in the spellbook make people have to gain new ways, and have to actually RUN somewhat.
Make it so people have to work for their items
Level out the skills so you can make as much as you can pking to balance it out.[/quote]
To add on to this you should really highlight that fact that we have runes for magic commands… make that spell book require runes to teleport & require higher levels for different teleporting. I think this would help a lot seeing as runes are basically useless now a days on rsps and take away from runecrafting as a result.

Also please don’t make teleports lead to Bosses & other strong npcs, people should walk to them. This will decrease the number of people wearing “rare” items or really high level items.

Read full topic
